{"lemma":"بَلْدَةُ","slug":"بَلْدَةُ","root":"ب.ل.د","root_slug":"ب-ل-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَلْدَة","root":"بلد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3166","n3167"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"town, city"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"place, village, community"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"township"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From بَلَد (balad) + ـَة (-a)."},"ipa":["/bal.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3166","headword_ar":"بَلْدَةٌ","root":"bld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino lamo","text_ar":"اـِنْ لَمْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tafoEalo ka*aA fahiYa balodapN bayoniY wa bayonika","text_ar":"تَفْعَلْ كَذَا فَهِىَ بَلْدَةٌ بَيْنِى وَ بَيْنِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If thou do not thus, it will be"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a cause of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"separation between me and thee;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * A, TA;) i. e., I will alienate thee from me so that a country, or region, shall separate us, each from the other. (A, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterless desert, in which one cannot find his way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any extensive tract of land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, L.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiytuhu bibalodapi A_iSomati","text_ar":"لَقِيتُهُ بِبَلْدَةِ اـِصْمَتِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"met him, in a desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desolate, place, in which there was no one beside."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Smt","text_ar":"صمت"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One of the Mansions of the Moon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) [namely,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Twenty-first Mansion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a patch of the sky,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"containing no stars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"containing only small stars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEaAy^im","text_ar":"نَعَايِم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEod Al*~aAbiH","text_ar":"سَعْد الذَّابِح"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) sometimes the moon declines from it, and takes as its mansion the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qilaAdap","text_ar":"قِلَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": it [app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqlAdp","text_ar":"القلادة"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the K, but accord. to the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albldp","text_ar":"البلدة"},{"kind":"text","text":",] consists of six stars resembling a bow, (K,) in the sign of Sagittarius ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawos","text_ar":"القَوْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (T:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albldp","text_ar":"البلدة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the Mansions of the Moon, consisting of six stars of Sagittarius"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqws","text_ar":"القوس"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which the sun enters on the shortest day of the year:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manaAzilu Alqamar","text_ar":"مَنَازِلُ القَمَر"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nzl","text_ar":"نزل"},{"kind":"text","text":": in the K it is also said that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albaladu","text_ar":"البَلَدُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a Mansion of the Moon; but this appears to be a mistake, occasioned by the accidental omission of the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; though"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albaladu","text_ar":"البَلَدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"would seem to be an appropriate name for the mansion next after the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nEAy^m","text_ar":"نعايم"},{"kind":"text","text":":] IF says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an asterism,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najomN","text_ar":"نَجْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said to be the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balodap","text_ar":"بَلْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast, of the Lion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"not meaning the mansion thus called in the sign of Sagittarius: El-Hareeree finds fault with him for using this expression, [the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bldp","text_ar":"بلدة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Lion,] but Ibn-Dhafr replies that it occurs in the language. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balodapN","text_ar":"بَلْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b5-  Also (S, M, L, TA, [in the K ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balad","text_ar":"بَلَد","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", by the accidental omission of the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit between the two collar-bones, with the part around it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of that pit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"third of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falak","text_ar":"فَلَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"(which are six in number)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of that part of a horse's breast which is called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawur","text_ar":"زَوُر"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHaY Alz~awori","text_ar":"رَحَى الزَّوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) or [so accord. to the M, but accord. to the K “and,”] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sador","text_ar":"صَدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, K,) of a camel, (M, A,) or of that which has a foot like the camel's, and of a solid-hoofed animal, (M,) and of a man: (A:) and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part immediately beneath the two prominent portions of flesh of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending to the arms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L.) Dhu-rRummeh says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^uniyxato faA^aloqato balodapF fawoqa balodapK"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was made to lie down, and threw"},{"kind":"text","text":"her"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tract of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN waAsiEu Albalodapi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ وَاسِعُ البَلْدَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is wide in the breast."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b6-  Also (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palm of the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":248},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, TA. [In the K, by the accidental omission of the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albalodapu","text_ar":"البَلْدَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", this meaning is assigned to ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba balodatahu EalaY balodatihi","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ بَلْدَتَهُ عَلَى بَلْدَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smote the palm of his hand upon his breast."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bulodapN","text_ar":"بُلْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places:       -A3-  and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAdapN","text_ar":"بَلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["M","K","T","S","A"]},{"entry_id":"n3167","headword_ar":"بُلْدَةٌ","root":"bld","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balodapN","text_ar":"بَلْدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baladN","text_ar":"بَلَدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balida","text_ar":"بَلِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clearness, from hair, of the space between the eyebrows:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bulojapN","text_ar":"بُلْجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bulojapN","text_ar":"بُلْجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the eyebrows not joined:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or ↓ the second signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space between the eyebrows."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b2-  And the first, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"form, aspect, appearance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lineaments,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the face. (K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAdapN","text_ar":"بَلَادَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","L","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}